&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo airmon-ng start wlan0
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>Switch the wireless interface to monitor mode, if it didn&amp;rsquo;t happen in previous steps to start captureing traffic.&lt;/p>
