&lt;h3 id="9-decoding-captured-files-hash-to-real-password">9. Decoding captured file&amp;rsquo;s hash to real password
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Finally, let&amp;rsquo;s do a password strength test using Hashcat. I will be testing this on my Macbook Pro 16 2021 with M1 Pro GPU and i7-8700 + RX 6600 XT using macOS Sonoma (Hackintosh)&lt;/p>
