&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hashcat -m &lt;span class="m">22000&lt;/span> dump.hc22000 -a &lt;span class="m">3&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;?d?d?d?d?d?d?d?d&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>where:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>-m 22000&lt;/code> specifies the WPA-PBKDF2-PMKID+EAPOL algorithm.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>-a 3&lt;/code> indicates a mask attack.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>&amp;quot;?d&amp;quot;&lt;/code> represents a digit.&lt;/li>
