&lt;h3 id="router-firmware-update">Router Firmware Update
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Vendors publish updates to fix vulnerabilities. Keeping the firmware updated improves security.&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="monitor-connected-devices">Monitor Connected Devices
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Periodically &lt;strong>look&lt;/strong> and see what devices are connected to your network to find unauthorized access.&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="phishing">Phishing
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://yegormi.github.io/post/why-most-wi-fi-networks-are-insecure/img/phishing.webp"
width="1920"
height="1080"
